WEBVTT

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:11.000
At the start of each pay period, you are required to manually create a new timesheet to keep track of your hours. 

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Be sure to review your organization's guidelines on when the pay period begins. 

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:20.000
To create a new timesheet, click the Create Timesheet icon. 

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:26.000
The Time - Create Timesheet page will appear, prompting you to create a new timesheet for the time period.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:37.000
If you want to change the time period, you have two options: you can either type in the date directly or click the Calendar icon to open the calendar and select the desired date.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Click the Save button to confirm your changes. 

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:44.000
Upon saving, you will be taken to the new timesheet.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
You can preview a timesheet from the following locations. 

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Timesheets are read-only when previewing them. 

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:09.000
To preview a timesheet, click the Magnifying Glass icon next to the timesheet you want to view or click the Preview button. 

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:16.000
At the top of the page, you'll see the current pay period and the status of your timesheet. 

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:31.000
The most common timesheet statuses you will encounter include INUSE (you're currently editing the timesheet), SUBMITTED (youâ€™re awaiting approval), APPROVING (approval is in progress), and EXTRACTED (processed by Payroll). 

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:38.000
If you have questions about other statuses you may receive, please contact your organization's Payroll department. 

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:42.000
You can also print your timesheet by clicking the Print Friendly icon.

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:53.000
Near the bottom of the page is the Approval History dropdown menu, which shows the approval history of the selected timesheet, including information about when the timesheet's status was updated. 

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:07.000
You can edit a timesheet in the following locations. 

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:15.000
To edit a timesheet, click the Pencil icon next to the timesheet you want to edit or click the Edit button. 

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:22.000
For detailed instructions on how to enter hours please refer to the Time - Current Page video.

